{"abstract": "The investment bank and its jailed ex-leader, Andr\u00e9 Esteves, illustrate why investors in companies that issue multiple classes of stock should note the risk.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/04/business/dealbook/btg-pactual-and-the-perils-of-supervoting-stock.html", "snippet": "The investment bank and its jailed ex-leader, Andr\u00e9 Esteves, illustrate why investors in companies that issue multiple classes of stock should note the risk.", "lead_paragraph": "BTG Pactual offers a case against companies issuing multiple classes of stock. The investment bank\u2019s former boss, Andr\u00e9 Esteves, who is incarcerated, has ceded voting control in a stock swap with his partners. It\u2019s a neat fix, but reveals yet another risk of supervoting stock. Investors in companies with similar structures \u2014 like Google, Moelis & Company and nearly every major media firm \u2014 should take heed.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/28/business/28DB-PACTUAL/28DB-PACTUAL-articleLarge-v2.jpg", "height": 541, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/11/28/business/28DB-PACTUAL/28DB-PACTUAL-articleLarge-v2.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 541}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/28/business/28DB-PACTUAL/28DB-PACTUAL-jumbo-v2.jpg", "height": 923, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/28/business/28DB-PACTUAL/28DB-PACTUAL-superJumbo-v2.jpg", "height": 1575, "width": 1748, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/28/business/28D